               </did>
               <scopecontent>
                  <p>Last entry of session minutes. At the end of the volume are a subscription list (1843) with names and amounts, and Annual Meeting minutes (Nov. 16, 1833-Nov. 12, 1837, five entries: election of trustees and financial actions).</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c02>
